{"tid":1739124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"To Mon Po 狗: 認真, 剛剛搵到文獻, 原來美軍測試過, 二噁英可致\"不舉\"","createTime":"2019-11-19T13:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T08:11:29.000Z","uid":269706,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"28c3ffda1503bf4481e97d7d4db074779c379a9a","tid":1739124,"uid":269706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:03:49.000Z","msg":"To Mon Po 狗: 認真, 剛剛搵到文獻, 原來美軍測試過, 二噁英可致&quot;不舉&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">知唔知咩叫&quot;費城實驗&quot;?<br />\n知唔知咩係&quot;Tesla&quot;? </span><br />\n<br />\n唔係車呀!!! <span style=\"color: gold;\">係&quot;nikola tesla&quot;</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%89%B9%E6%96%AF%E6%8B%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%2596%25AF%25E6%258B%2589&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=81c462de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%89%B9%E6%96%AF%E6%8B%89</a><br />\n<br />\n當年美軍偷左狂人科學家Tesla既料, 走去做實驗. <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">結果班美軍痴晒線, <br />\n有D唔知點解夾住喺塊石屎中間</span><br />\n<br />\n唯一解釋係高能量令石屎分解再結合...<br />\n<br />\n而有一樣副作用係美軍唔會講, 就係高能量令陽具入面個條根頂唔順 = <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不舉</span></span>....<br />\n自此美國就輸出可合成二噁英既武器俾其他國家, 令佢地既軍人DNA逐步減少.....<br />\n中共都係抄美國野, 但係識條撚咩<br />\n<br />\nMON PO狗, 知點解前線唔理照火魔啦!!!!!!    <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依家知咩叫攬抄啦!!!! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n同狗攬抄既幫推~~~~"},{"pid":"5fed9949bceee6dd375ea324054ad4eb02ba1741","tid":1739124,"uid":27027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:05:12.000Z","msg":"來吧狗仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7d4f6b1934897836d26d149e1bfce694352ed0","tid":1739124,"uid":116054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:05:17.000Z","msg":"搞搞下想自製送俾狗"},{"pid":"fdf2de095fe5d5a42adb59f956219